'''Koffi Gahou''' (22 Ukwakira 1947 - 24 Kanama 2019) yari umuhanzi, umukinnyi wa filime, n'umuyobozi<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes/?no=6107</ref>.

== Ubuzima ==
Gahou yavukiye i Cotonou ku ya 22 Ukwakira 1947. Yize kuva 1986 kugeza 1989 mu kigo cy’ubushakashatsi bw’ikinamico muri Kaminuza ya Sorbonne Nouvelle Paris 3<ref>https://matinlibre.com/2019/08/26/benin-le-monde-culturel-pleure-koffi-gahou/</ref>, abona uruhushya rwo kwigisha. Kuva mu 1985 kugeza 1986 Gahou yakoraga umwuga wo kwimenyereza  muri Conservatoire national supérieur d'art ikinamico i Paris maze mu 1988, yimenyereza umwuga muri Institut international de la marionnette<ref>https://actubenin.com/carnet-noirlartiste-koffi-gahou-nest-plus</ref>.  Guhera mu 1974, yize ubwe mu buhanzi bwa plastiki, imashini zometse ku rukuta, amashusho, ndetse n’imbere<ref>https://lanouvelletribune.info/2019/08/benin-lartiste-koffi-gahou-nest-plus/</ref>. Gahou yinjiye mu bakozi ba Leta nk'umuhanzi kandi akora ibitaramo mu itsinda rya "Cerveaux noirs". Yashinze kandi itsinda ry’ikinamico "Zama Hara"<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0229234/characters/nm0301121</ref>, yagize imurikagurisha ryinshi ry’ibikorwa bye muri [[Afurika]], [[Uburayi]], Cuba, na [[Amerika]].<ref>https://www.telerama.fr/personnalite/koffi-gahou,581100.php</ref> 

Gahou yakoze imyenda "Yovo Helou e, Akowe helou e" mu 1990. Irerekana imbata zifatanije amaboko inyuma, kandi byari byiza cyane<ref>https://www.theatre-contemporain.net/biographies/Koffi-Gahou/</ref>. Mu 2000, Gahou yakinnye murumuna wa Boubacar, umuhinzi, muri film ya Jean Odoutan ''Barbecue Pejo''<ref>https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/g11h84q5f68?hl=es</ref> . 

Mu mashusho ya videwo muri Mata 2019, Gahou yasabye ko yishyurwa miliyoni 30 z’amafaranga CFA y’umudepite wo muri Bénine yategetswe kumuha n’Urugereko rwa 3 rw’ubucuruzi rw’urukiko rwa Cotonou<ref>https://www.franceinter.fr/personnes/koffi-gahou</ref>. Iki kibazo cyaturutse mu marushanwa yo mu 2007 Gahou yatsinze ariko ntiyabona amafaranga yigihembo. <ref>https://www.senscritique.com/contact/Koffi_Gahou/78137</ref>Gahou yapfuye ku ya 24 Kanama 2019 i Abomey . Umuhango wo kumushyingura wabaye ku ya 25 Nzeri<ref>https://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne_gen_cpersonne=83887.html</ref>. 

